Type Parameters:
V - The type of the value in the association.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Composite<Sequence<Association<String,V>>>, Sequential<Association<String,V>>, Comparable<Sequence<Association<String,V>>>, Iterable<Association<String,V>>
public final class Dictionary<V> extends AssociativeCollection<String,V>
This collection class is a convenience class that implements an associative collection whose keys are always of type String. The implementation dynamically scales up and down the size of the underlying data structures as the number elements changes over time.
Author:
Derk Norton
